str2: To change my place (abode), leave, depart, remove, pass over. From meta and the base of basis; to change place.
Thence, from that place. From ekei; thence.

Personal / Possessive Pronoun - Genitive Masculine 3rd Person Plural
str2: He, she, it, they, them, same. From the particle au; the reflexive pronoun self, used of the third person, and of the other persons.
From sunago; an assemblage of persons; specially, a Jewish 'synagogue'; by analogy, a Christian church.
